			<h1>Science in the Service of Animal Welfare</h1>
<p class="intro">UFAW is an internationally recognised, independent, scientific and educational animal welfare charity concerned with improving knowledge and understanding of animals&rsquo; needs. It promotes high standards of welfare and practical, long-lasting solutions to welfare problems for farm, companion, laboratory, captive wild animals and those with which we interact in the wild.</p>
		</div>
